if you look like one.

05:21.543 --> 05:22.743
Anyway, I was pretty lonely,

05:22.745 --> 05:24.612
so I had to make up
my own stories and games,

05:24.614 --> 05:25.913
and I promised myself

05:25.915 --> 05:28.082
if I ever made
any friends that...

05:28.084 --> 05:30.518
